<s> More interesting - what should I do with new members, i.e. version histories of which were not in bindings of previous version of collection.  </s>
<s> Should I create versioned-resource to provide workspace,version-history - versioned-resource binding?  </s>
<s> But which version should this versioned-resource select by checkedIn/checkedOut property?  </s>
